 of negative cash flow and to begin turning a profit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Poor management of finances can lead to various problems such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Failure to collect your accounts receivable<\/li><li>Running out of money unexpectedly<\/li><li>Making late payments to suppliers<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"digital-money-management-solutions-to-help-keep-your-business-agile\"><\/span>Digital Money Management Solutions to Help Keep Your Business Agile<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"274\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/digital-money-management-640x274-1.jpg\" alt=\"digital money management\" class=\"wp-image-857\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/digital-money-management-640x274-1.jpg 640w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/digital-money-management-640x274-1-300x128.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The best money management tricks in the world won\u2019t help you if you don\u2019t have financial management software to help you keep track of your finances. Below is a look at some of the top money management software that can help you manage your <a href=\"https:\/\/verv.novatti.com\/business-account\/#:~:text=BUSINESS%20ACCOUNT-,Corporate%20Accounts,-With%20VERV%2C%20being\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Verv Corporate Accounts.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-mint-its-free-and-offers-cashflow-insights\"><\/span>1. Mint \u2013 It\u2019s Free and Offers Cashflow Insights<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mint is not only the most downloaded personal finance software, but it\u2019s also a free <a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/sites\/forbesbusinesscouncil\/2021\/04\/01\/aspiring-entreprene